preference.name: ARM_saveas_item
preference.preference_description: Activates the Teamcenter's "Save As" performance transaction. This measures the elapsed time from the beginning of the operation to the display of all objects. Valid Values: * ON: Enables performance monitoring of the "Save As" performance transaction. * OFF: Suppresses performance monitoring of the "Save As" performance transaction.
